public abstract class DmoExtGWTWrapperBase<DMO extends DmcObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.data.Model, com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.data.ModelData

The DmoExtGWTWrapperBase provides a common base class for auto generated Dark Matter Wrapper (DMW) objects that allow Dark MAtter Objects (DMOs) to be used ExtGWT data models.
